## --- Watching login/logout
# {{{

# Watching other users
watch=(notme)
# Check every 60 seconds.
LOGCHECK=60
# Format message printed on login/logout
WATCHFMT="%(a:${fg[blue]}Hello %n [%m] [%t]:${fg[red]}Bye %n [%m] [%t])"

# }}}

